1. Two States: Buy and Upgrade
2. Buy: The max number of servers is 25, buy 25 8GB servers
3. Once all servers are bought, upgrade all servers to 16GB
4. Double RAM every time
5. Make sure the script can be run at any time, post buy phase and mid upgrade phase
6. When in upgrade phase, check for lowest RAM server and upgrade it,
    loop until all servers are same level.
    - This needs to be done every time the script is run
    - to get everything back in sync
7. When all servers are same leel, upgrade all servers to next level